messages.message: without getting into the weeds on config. But I feel like a number of PR’s have hit this message lately
Yeah I currently see almost every PR hitting it :/

The travis PR diff-ing code (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/master/shared-utils/build-utils/shared/src/py/run_tests_for_affected_code.py) to figure out which unit tests to run is currently broken. Not sure who has bandwidth to take a look at why that’s not working. But until then, we end up running all python tests, which will often timeout the run
